PROFESSIONAL PRODUCT SUPPORT SERVICES. RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT EXPENSES INCREASED $183 MILLION OR 11%, PRIMARILY DRIVEN BY INCREASED HEADCOUNT-RELATED EXPENSES.

