THAT OUR BOARD OF DIRECTORS AUTHORIZED TWO NEW SHARE REPURCHASE PROGRAMS: A $20.0 BILLION TENDER OFFER, WHICH WAS COMPLETED ON AUGUST 17, 2006; AND AUTHORIZATION FOR UP TO AN ADDITIONAL $20.0 BILLION ONGOING SHARE REPURCHASE PROGRAM WITH AN

