NOTE 12    UNEARNED REVENUE

UNEARNED REVENUE IS COMPRISED OF THE FOLLOWING

ITEMS.

VOLUME LICENSING PROGRAMS

 REPRESENTS CUSTOMER BILLINGS FOR MULTI-YEAR LICENSING ARRANGEMENTS, PAID EITHER UPFRONT OR ANNUALLY AT

THE BEGINNING OF EACH BILLING COVERAGE PERIOD, WHICH ARE ACCOUNTED FOR AS SUBSCRIPTIONS WITH REVENUE RECOGNIZED RATABLY OVER THE BILLING COVERAGE PERIOD.

PAGE

