(GENERALLY THREE TO FIVE YEARS) USING THE STRAIGHT-LINE METHOD. THE FAIR VALUE OF EACH AWARD GRANT IS ESTIMATED ON THE DATE OF GRANT USING THE FOLLOWING ASSUMPTIONS.

